<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Rolex Reviews</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/styles.css">
  <style>
    /* General page styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .hero {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        height: 60vh;
        background: url('https://media.rolex.com/image/upload/q_auto:eco/f_auto/c_limit,w_1920/v1708385821/rolexcom/about-rolex/hub/about-rolex-hub-cover-aca202310cw-0002') no-repeat center center/cover;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 60px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .hero p {
        font-size: 18px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    .content {
        display: flex;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .content h2 {
        font-size: 32px;
        color: #006837;
        flex: 1;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content .text {
        flex: 2;
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .content .text strong {
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Reviews container for horizontal scrolling */
    .reviews-container {
        display: flex;
        gap: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px;
        animation: marquee 60s linear infinite; /* Adjusted speed */
        width: max-content; /* Ensure the container adjusts to the total width of the cards */
        flex-shrink: 0; /* Prevent shrinking of the container */
    }

    /* Animation for scrolling cards */
    @keyframes marquee {
      0% {
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
      100% {
        transform: translateX(-100%);
      }
    }

    /* Individual review card styles */
    .review-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        width: 300px;  /* Fixed width for landscape */
        height: 180px; /* Fixed height for landscape */
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        transition: transform 60s linear infinite;;
        flex-shrink: 0; /* Prevent shrinking of individual cards */
    }

    .review-card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .review-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .review-body {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .review-user {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }
  
    /* Button to Add a Review */
    .add-review-btn {
        display: inline-block;  /* Change from block to inline-block */
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 16px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .add-review-btn:hover {
        background-color: #555;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/images/rolex.png" alt="Rolex Logo">
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="http://localhost:3000/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://localhost:3000/watches">Watches</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://localhost:3000/about-rolex">About Rolex</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">The Rolex Experience</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://localhost:3000/login">Login</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <div class="search">
            <a href="http://localhost:3000/find-store"><p>Find A Store</p></a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="hero">
        <div>
            <p>BEHIND THE CROWN</p>
            <h1>About Rolex</h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>An unrivalled reputation for quality and expertise</h2>
        <div class="text">
            <p><strong>Rolex is an integrated and independent Swiss watch manufacture.</strong> Headquartered in Geneva, it is recognized for its expertise and the quality of its products.</p>
            <p>Hans Wilsdorf, founder of the company, instilled a notion of perpetual excellence, leading to major watchmaking innovations, such as the Oyster, the first waterproof wristwatch and the Perpetual rotor self-winding mechanism...</p>
        </div>
    </div>

  <h1 style="text-align: center; padding: 20px;">Rolex User Reviews</h1>

  <!-- Container to scroll through reviews -->
  <div class="reviews-container">
    <% userReviews.forEach(review => { %>
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-title"><%= review.title %></div>
        <div class="review-body"><%= review.body %></div>
        <div class="review-user">- <%= review.user %></div>
      </div>
    <% }); %>
  </div>

    <a href="http://localhost:3000/submit-review" class="add-review-btn">Add Review</a>

</body>
</html>
